,0.056406],"unified_progress":[0.034527,0.069673,0.088921,0.10032,0.10688,0.10496,0.10234,0.097258,0.09556,0.081349,0.066729,0.051476]},{"section":11,"text":"Putting this together, a sudden onset of a lump with perimenstrual symptoms makes me think of fibroadenomas or perhaps a simple breast cyst.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.037364,0.06795,0.079258,0.086803,0.092061,0.093641,0.095651,0.094232,0.091134,0.089245,0.086428,0.086233],"unified_progress":[0.03777,0.066069,0.078278,0.087956,0.092295,0.094724,0.094962,0.094426,0.094135,0.089057,0.086118,0.084211]},{"section":12,"text":"Fibroadenomas are benign tumors of the breast and are often associated with cyclical symptoms.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032989,0.057363,0.073065,0.084815,0.095515,0.099975,0.10805,0.10732,0.101,0.091515,0.079473,0.06892],"unified_progress":[0.031574,0.059834,0.082568,0.095088,0.10131,0.1121,0.10531,0.10101,0.097461,0.08689,0.071102,0.055758]},{"section":13,"text":"They are usually firm, movable, and can vary in size.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03765,0.066367,0.081158,0.089134,0.095105,0.096495,0.10073,0.099152,0.095848,0.086448,0.081247,0.070672],"unified_progress":[0.046949,0.078191,0.089006,0.095734,0.10147,0.10094,0.098694,0.09658,0.093125,0.083286,0.06658,0.049443]},{"section":14,"text":"However, they are more common in younger women, though not exclusively.","dimension":0,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033746,0.056534,0.070377,0.078929,0.089604,0.094679,0.10196,0.10486,0.1061,0.10195,0.090358,0.070891],"unified_progress":[0.037575,0.063742,0.078765,0.086821,0.096552,0.1004,0.10089,0.10302,0.099882,0.099333,0.079329,0.053691]},{"section":15,"text":"Wait, but she's 50, which is around the age when breast density starts to decrease, making cysts more common.","dimension":11,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038689,0.069897,0.080004,0